WEBVTT

00:09:59.041 --> 00:10:01.154
but this is not just about Egypt.

00:10:01.601 --> 00:10:04.803
Polarization is on the rise
in the whole world.

00:10:05.325 --> 00:10:07.899
We need to work hard on figuring out

00:10:07.923 --> 00:10:11.244
how technology could be
part of the solution,

00:10:11.268 --> 00:10:13.278
rather than part of the problem.

00:10:15.072 --> 00:10:18.412
There's a lot of debate today
on how to combat online harassment

00:10:18.436 --> 00:10:19.658
and fight trolls.

00:10:19.992 --> 00:10:21.460
This is so important.

00:10:21.818 --> 00:10:23.671
No one could argue against that.

00:10:24.251 --> 00:10:29.468
But we need to also think about how
to design social media experiences

00:10:29.492 --> 00:10:32.671
that promote civility
and reward thoughtfulness.